Text/ETSV version 0.01
======================

 This module is used to manipulate ETSV (Enhanced Tab Separated Values).

INSTALLATION

 To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

 This module requires perl5.8 or later.
 And,
 this module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Exporter

